target": {"title_area": {"text": "金龙鱼回应油罐车事件，公司对食用油运输有严格监管，不会使用别家的油罐车，具体情况如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月 9 日，针对「油罐车运输乱象」事件，金龙鱼工作人员向记者回应表示，工厂的食用油都是在自己工厂进行桶装之后再运输的，公司对食用油运输有严格监管，贯彻执行国家有关法律法规对食用油运输的相关规定。集团旗下各工厂都是遵循管理制度，不会使用别家的油罐车，食用油的运输工具必须按照《食用植物油散装运输规范》要求，以确保产品质量安全。（北京商报）金龙鱼回应油罐车事件：公司对食用油运输有严格监管 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-85e8006c6565eee699e9e717fede806f_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "258 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661162511"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIlafUrbe54K5dEAMaCTEwOTIwMjU0MiDOnbS0BjAAOIABQANyCTY2MTE2MjUxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1720533951.894875", "card_id": "Q_661057913", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "自己的哥哥是皇帝，称之为「皇兄」；如果自己的弟弟是皇帝，应该如何称呼？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-80fc1206fe766c9cf17fe765b77a0cfe_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "127 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661057913"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlafUrbe54K5dEAMaCTEwOTE3OTM0MSDiq660BjAAODhABHIJNjYxMDU3OTEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1720533951.895092", "card_id": "Q_661136473", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "fee